partnerDetails.about:
NA Technologies is an Information Security & Systems integration-focused company. We provide industry-leading information security solutions and offer various products of world-renowned brands for our solutions

NA Technologies have a strong team and solutions for ELV division and We offer the following solutions for ELV domain;
1.	Data transmission IT Networks; Local Area Networks(LAN) using Fiber Optic, Copper or Wireless.
2.	Telephone (PABX) :Voice & Video.  
3.	CCTV/ IP Surveillance.
4.	Fire Alarm System ( Addressable & Conventional System).
5.	Time Attendance & Access Control System.
6.	Public Address Broadcasting.
